Governor Yahaya Bello of Kogi State on Monday took oath of office for second tenure. The second inauguration took place in Lokoja, Kogi State capital.
Governor Bello and the Deputy Governor, Edward Onoja, both of who were declared winner of the November 2019 violent governorship election were administered oath of office and oath of allegiance by the Chief Justice of Kogi State.

			
